by lyrixx at 2016-04-04T19:58:36Z

I just pushed some code to integrate the component and the Full Stack Framework.

Now, you can use:
```yaml
framework:
    workflows:
        my_workflow:
            marking_store:
                type: property_accessor
            supports:
                - Some\Class
            places:
                - first
                - last
            transitions:
                go:
                    from:
                        - first
                    to:
                        - last
```

and a new service `workflow.my_workflown` ; and some goodness in twig ;)

